* Updated the standard kernels to Linux-2.6.31.6 with btrfs update from 2.6.32
* Added Grub2-beta (version 1.97.1), Grub-legacy (0.97) is still there anyway
* Patched parted-1.9.0 to fix multiple problems (GParted bug 601574)
* Updated gparted to version 0.5.0 (adds support for Linux software RAID)
* dmraid-1.0.0-rc16 fixes (Gentoo bug #275451)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
