* Updated lvm2 to 2.02.51 (Logical Volume Manager version 2)
* Updated xorg-server to version 1.6.3.901 (graphical server and drivers)
* Support for framebuffer video in the standard kernels (boot option "vga=xxx")
* Replaced Xvesafb with Xfbdev (run "wizard" to use this graphical mode)
